                <a href="" id="installation" name=”installation” class="anchor"></a>
                <h2>Installation</h2>
                <p>We recommend to use <a href="http://www.getcomposer.org">Composer</a> in order to create a new project.</p>
                <p>Once installed, run the following commands to create a new project:</p>
                <pre>
                    <code>$ composer.phar create-project -s dev --prefer-dist --dev knplabs/rad-edition my_project<br />$ cd my_project</code>
                </pre>
                </div>
            </div>
